### Job Skill Controller Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills

### 1. Create a new Job Skill - Java
POST http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Java",
  "category": "PROGRAMING_LANGUAGE"
}

### 2. Create Job Skill - Spring Boot
POST http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Spring Boot",
  "category": "FRAMEWORK"
}

### 3. Create Job Skill - PostgreSQL
POST http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "PostgreSQL",
  "category": "DATABASE"
}

### 4. Create Job Skill - AWS
POST http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "AWS",
  "category": "CLOUD_PLATFORM"
}

### 5. Create Job Skill - Docker
POST http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Docker",
  "category": "DEVOPS"
}

### 6. Create Job Skill - Python
POST http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Python",
  "category": "PROGRAMING_LANGUAGE"
}

### 7. Get all Job Skills
GET http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills

### 8. Get Job Skill by ID (1)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/1

### 9. Get Job Skill by ID (2)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/2

### 10. Get Job Skill by ID (3)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/3

### 11. Get Job Skill by ID (4)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/4

### 12. Get Job Skill by ID (5)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/5

### 13. Update Job Skill (1) - Java to Java Enterprise
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Java Enterprise",
  "category": "PROGRAMING_LANGUAGE"
}

### 14. Update Job Skill (2) - Spring Boot to Spring Boot 3
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Spring Boot 3",
  "category": "FRAMEWORK"
}

### 15. Update Job Skill (3) - PostgreSQL to PostgreSQL Advanced
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "PostgreSQL Advanced",
  "category": "DATABASE"
}

### 16. Delete Job Skill (6)
DELETE http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/6

### 17. Get all Job Skills after deletion
GET http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills

### 18. Try to get deleted skill (should fail)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/6

### 19. Try to create duplicate skill (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Java Enterprise",
  "category": "PROGRAMING_LANGUAGE"
}

### 20. Try to update to duplicate name (should fail)
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Java Enterprise",
  "category": "CLOUD_PLATFORM"
}

### 21. Try to create skill without name (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "category": "PROGRAMING_LANGUAGE"
}

### 22. Try to create skill without category (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "SomeSkill"
}

### 23. Try to get non-existent skill (should fail)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/job-skills/999
